cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.SI 

The paper discusses supervised speech separation using deep learning, which involves signal processing, machine learning, and acoustic modeling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper may also fall under cs.SI (Speech Recognition and Synthesis) and cs.MM (Multimedia), as it deals with speech separation and audio processing.
